{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_04_02",
  "title": "成宮すず 2話 勘違い、ふたたび",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お、いたいた。すず、打ち上げの話なんだけど――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ there you are. Suzu‚ about the after-party――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "先日のライブが終わってから、なんだか、こう……\n距離が近い気がするんですわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since the other day's live‚ it feels like…\nWe've become closer‚ haven't we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9316683678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "私から話し掛けると\nやけに優しい笑顔で応じてくれますし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I speak to you‚\nyou respond with an unusually gentle smile…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "おーい、すず？　誰の話をしてるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Suzu? Who are you talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "やはり……私に恋心を……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could it be… you've developed feelings of love… for me!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "おーい。すずー……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey. Suzuー…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "確かに私は、今回のライブで\n麻奈様の曲を見事に歌い上げましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed‚ at the recent live‚\nI perfectly performed Mana-sama's song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "私の堂々たる歌いっぷりを見て\n惚れてしまったのでは……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having seen my magnificent singing‚\ncould it be that you've fallen for me…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ダメだ、全然聞いてないな……\nあ、そうだ。あれを試してみるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No use‚ she's not listening at all…\nAh‚ that's right. Maybe I should try that thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.0786316531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "トリビュートライブ前は告白されたと勘違いしましたが\n今度はちゃんと理由もありますし、間違いないですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mistook it for a confession before the tribute live‚\nbut this time there's a definite reason‚ it can't be a mistake!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3833332379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、渚から借りた小説のセリフにも\nありましたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ there was a line in the novel\nI borrowed from Nagisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2649871261,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "「言葉にした想いが全てではない」……と！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Not all feelings need to be expressed in words\"…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、最近ずっと私の胸が\nもやもやしているのは一体なぜなのでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ I wonder why my heart\nhas been feeling this fuzzy lately?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "……きっと、最近忙しくて\n焼肉を食べていないせいですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It must be because I've been so busy recently\nthat I haven't had any yakiniku!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.470496114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あったあった。これなら気付くかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Found it‚ found it. Maybe she'll notice this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2038294474,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 2698.966980000009,
          "startTime": 87.9027964274
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "はっ！　この音は……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh! That sound is… wait‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.8038294474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！？\nいいい、いつからそこにいましたの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!?\nH-h-how long have you been there!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.8959009715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "ぬ、盗み聞きとは感心しませんわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eavesdropping isn't very commendable‚ you know!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0371627807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いや、結構前からいたんだけど……。まさか\n俺の声よりポテトチップスの袋の音で気付くとはな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I've been here for a while… I didn't expect\nyou'd notice me by the sound of a potato chip bag rather than my voice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1251001823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "なんですの、その気付かせ方は！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What a way to get my attention!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6038294474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "……それで、なんのご用ですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ what do you want?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.870496114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そうそう。打ち上げの話なんだが、候補を\nいくつかまとめたよ。すずは行きたい店はあるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ right. About the after-party‚\nI’ve compiled some options. Do you have a place in mind you want to go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1390843074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "ええっと、確認なんですが……\n焼肉は私達二人で行くんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ just to confirm…\nAre we going to have yakiniku just the two of us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8400427959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　そのつもりだけど……\n他のみんなも連れて行きたいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? That was the plan…\nDo you want to invite everyone else too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5038294474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そういう訳ではありませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ that’s not what I mean!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.270496114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわ、今の私は麻奈様の曲を歌いあげた\n『二代目星降る奇跡』……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed‚ now I am the one who sang Mana's song‚\nthe \"Second Miracle Star Descending\"…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3080777954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "禁断の恋心だって寛大に受け止めてあげませんと！\nファイトですわ、私！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I must generously accept even forbidden feelings!\nFight on‚ me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.7942101449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "こほん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahem!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.370496114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-suz022.m4a",
      "text": "いいでしょう\n私と二人で焼肉に行くことを許可しますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Very well.\nI will permit us to go have yakiniku together‚ just the two of us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.2038294474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……ええと、今回練習で手助けしてくれたのは\n琴乃と芽衣と莉央さん、だよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So‚ the ones who helped out with practice this time were Kotono‚\nMei‚ and Rio-san‚ right?",
